{"tid":1698214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如你家中的老人家係藍C/廢老請盡阻止佢哋去投票","createTime":"2019-11-07T10:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:49:35.000Z","uid":110895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c982d6cff37c99918d54ccf67cb5e0d69d2c43","tid":1698214,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"首先你可以嘗試瘋狂遊說<br />\n盡量用理性方法令佢哋變黃<br />\n例如狂播片、DEFAULT 31/32台、刪走81 82 83台、理性分析時局、感性催淚洗腦等等<br />\n不過我知係好難...變得黃的話早就黃咗...唔使等而家...<br />\n所以請用第二手準備: 阻佢投票...<br />\n可以投票果日自己早早去咗投先再同佢哋出街...<br />\n或者一齊去做其他嘢之類~等佢冇時間投票...<br />\n最極致就係收起佢張信甚至身份證之類...<br />\n不過就真係唔好硬來...始終都係一家人...都係家中的長輩<br />\n口角都算就真係唔好動手動腳...<br />\n<br />\n利申: 家中<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">幾乎</span></span>全黃<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">(只有2個藍的長期唔喺香港)</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿婆本來藍...但被小弟成功洗<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">淺</span></span>黃...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢話果日唔投...都好GE...反正我都冇把握佢一定唔會投民賤聯...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88d559f20a1e5ce3c05d6d9da21588ca90232ea","tid":1698214,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"595c3a3f3e54a820ad7bc7805c4f565daf32d306","tid":1698214,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a25a9804f850136f4dd1c2a875d55ba19f52a684","tid":1698214,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}